CREDITS**: I make all our maps and have a number of them. If you like them stop by our server(204.17.65.211:27015). 


DESCRIPTION**: This map is a pretty dark map. Each side starts on opposite corners. There are catwalks above the center room. There are a number of bodies hung on meathooks in the center. Throughout there is alot of bodies and blood! There are two control centers in the center which if you shoot or use the keyboard it will let the outside rain in and light by opening two huge doors in the roof. Almost everything is walkable. try this one in low grav too.

BUGS: GIVEN I HAVE SO MANY BODIES ON MEATHOOKS YOU HAVE TO DISABLE GRENADES ON THIS ONE!!
